df: no file systems processed&lt;br/&gt;
 recovery-small test_58: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_58 failed with 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached two files:&lt;br/&gt;
recovery-small.test_58.tgz - tarball of the test_log files&lt;br/&gt;
recovery-small.test_58.test_log.service331.log.dbg: output of the test with shell debugging of &quot;set -x&quot;. The log showed the test passed, but it was a flase positive. The &apos;df&apos; failed with 1, yet a subsequent &quot;set +x&quot; set the return value to 0, thus gave a false positive. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
