                            <comment id="42698" author="hongchao.zhang" created="Fri, 3 Aug 2012 22:23:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Jay, the patch is updated as per your advice, thanks a lot!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42561" author="jaylan" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 14:58:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be nice if you can check the status of the first &apos;df&apos; command, and perform the second &apos;df&apos; only if the first returns failure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42560" author="jaylan" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 14:56:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;== recovery-small test 58: Eviction in the middle of open RPC reply processing ======================= 11:54:50 (1343847290)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;del&gt;rw-r&lt;/del&gt;&lt;del&gt;r&lt;/del&gt;- 1 root root 0 Aug  1 11:54 /mnt/nbp0-1/f58&lt;br/&gt;
