service337@o2ib:/lustre&lt;br/&gt;
                       3937056    209208   3527720   6% /mnt/nbp0-1&lt;br/&gt;
Resetting fail_loc on all nodes...done.&lt;br/&gt;
PASS 58 (40s)&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;From the above log, you can see the first &apos;df&apos; failed and the second &apos;df&apos; passed with &apos;df&apos; output!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42541" author="hongchao.zhang" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 06:50:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the possible patch is tracked at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3506&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3506&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hi Jay, Is this issue reproducible, and if so, could you please help to test with the patch?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42428" author="hongchao.zhang" created="Mon, 30 Jul 2012 06:53:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the eviction of this client is just caused by the revalidate request on the root inode of &quot;df&quot;, then this issue is triggered.&lt;br/&gt;
and this bug should be fixed by waiting some time before calling &quot;df&quot; or doing something else to trigger the evcition/recovery.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42417" author="pjones" created="Fri, 27 Jul 2012 21:09:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hongchao&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please look into this one?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
